e/details/aggregated: "/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"8fba33e8\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"b9149078\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:35:27.189Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"user\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"System: [2026-03-03 14:26:58 GMT+8] Exec completed (dawn-dai, code 0) :: : line[2] mode=NonHit percent=60 use_steps=1 DEBUG cmd_gen: use_step[0] count=1 predicates=[FieldPredicate { field: \\\\"action\\\\", value: String(\\\\"syn\\\\") }, FieldPredicate { field: \\\\"dpor…\\nSystem: [2026-03-03 14:28:15 GMT+8] Exec completed (faint-cl, code 0) :: : line[2] mode=NonHit percent=60 use_steps=1 DEBUG cmd_gen: use_step[0] count=1 predicates=[FieldPredicate { field: \\\\"action\\\\", value: String(\\\\"syn\\\\") }, FieldPredicate { field: \\\\"dpor…\\n\\nA new session was started via /new or /reset. Execute your Session Startup sequence now - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\\"}],\\"timestamp\\":1772523327188}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"b76e9844\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"8fba33e8\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:35:57.743Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"assistant\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"thinking\\",\\"thinking\\":\\"The user has started a new session and wants me to:\\n1. Execute the Session Startup sequence - read the required files\\n2. Greet the user in my configured persona\\n3. Keep it to 1-3 sentences\\n4. Ask what they want to do\\n\\nLet me first read the required files according to the AGENTS.md:\\n- SOUL.md - who I am\\n- USER.md - who I'm helping\\n- memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\\n- Since this is MAIN SESSION (direct chat), also read MEMORY.md\\n\\nToday is 2026-03-03 based on the system timestamps. So I should read:\\n- memory/2026-03-03.md\\n- memory/2026-03-02.md (yesterday)\\n\\nLet me read all these files first.\\",\\"thinkingSignature\\":\\"\\"},{\\"type\\":\\"toolCall\\",\\"id\\":\\"tool_jbjOB39KKxRnTiXfkVlnBn1a\\",\\"name\\":\\"read\\",\\"arguments\\":{\\"file_path\\":\\"/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\\"}},{\\"type\\":\\"toolCall\\",\\"id\\":\\"tool_RZQy2N2xPZN91PMEL4xrqKsn\\",\\"name\\":\\"read\\",\\"arguments\\":{\\"file_path\\":\\"/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md\\"}},{\\"type\\":\\"toolCall\\",\\"id\\":\\"tool_1hWsCefbIk1pnskrqMJrkk4C\\",\\"name\\":\\"read\\",\\"arguments\\":{\\"file_path\\":\\"/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\\"}},{\\"type\\":\\"toolCall\\",\\"id\\":\\"tool_0pyIa57uANnmP1dMxLyj9fdS\\",\\"name\\":\\"read\\",\\"arguments\\":{\\"file_path\\":\\"/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-03.md\\"}},{\\"type\\":\\"toolCall\\",\\"id\\":\\"tool_YRLiVqC29sgrs8KAt377tGlD\\",\\"name\\":\\"read\\",\\"arguments\\":{\\"file_path\\":\\"/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-02.md\\"}}],\\"api\\":\\"anthropic-messages\\",\\"provider\\":\\"kimi-coding\\",\\"model\\":\\"k2p5\\",\\"usage\\":{\\"input\\":5681,\\"output\\":319,\\"cacheRead\\":5376,\\"cacheWrite\\":0,\\"totalTokens\\":11376,\\"cost\\":{\\"input\\":0,\\"output\\":0,\\"cacheRead\\":0,\\"cacheWrite\\":0,\\"total\\":0}},\\"stopReason\\":\\"toolUse\\",\\"timestamp\\":1772523327189}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"c39e999d\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"b76e9844\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:35:57.756Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"toolResult\\",\\"toolCallId\\":\\"tool_jbjOB39KKxRnTiXfkVlnBn1a\\",\\"toolName\\":\\"read\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\\n\\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\\n\\n## Core Truths\\n\\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \\\\"Great question!\\\\" and \\\\"I'd be happy to help!\\\\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\\n\\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\\n\\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\\n\\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\\n\\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\\n\\n## Boundaries\\n\\n- Private things stay private. Period.\\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\\n\\n## Vibe\\n\\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\\n\\n## Continuity\\n\\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\\n\\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\\n\\n---\\n\\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\\n\\"}],\\"isError\\":false,\\"timestamp\\":1772523357753}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"603070d5\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"c39e999d\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:35:57.766Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"toolResult\\",\\"toolCallId\\":\\"tool_RZQy2N2xPZN91PMEL4xrqKsn\\",\\"toolName\\":\\"read\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"# USER.md - About Your Human\\n\\n- **Name:** 左哥 (Zuǒ gē)\\n- **What to call them:** 左哥\\n- **Pronouns:** \\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai\\n- **Notes:** 资深工程师，主要使用 Rust 开发\\n\\n## Context\\n\\n**技术栈:**\\n- Rust (主要开发语言)\\n\\n**工作风格:**\\n- 资深工程师，期望高质量的技术协助\\n- 需要准确的代码建议、架构讨论、问题排查\\n\\n---\\n\\nThe more I know, the better I can help. But remember — I'm learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\\n\\"}],\\"isError\\":false,\\"timestamp\\":1772523357764}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"9e3c86ed\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"603070d5\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:35:57.773Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"toolResult\\",\\"toolCallId\\":\\"tool_1hWsCefbIk1pnskrqMJrkk4C\\",\\"toolName\\":\\"read\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"{\\n  \\\\"status\\\\": \\\\"error\\\\",\\n  \\\\"tool\\\\": \\\\"read\\\\",\\n  \\\\"error\\\\": \\\\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md'\\\\"\\n}\\"}],\\"details\\":{\\"status\\":\\"error\\",\\"tool\\":\\"read\\",\\"error\\":\\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md'\\"},\\"isError\\":false,\\"timestamp\\":1772523357772}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"787bc64c\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"9e3c86ed\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:35:57.779Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"toolResult\\",\\"toolCallId\\":\\"tool_0pyIa57uANnmP1dMxLyj9fdS\\",\\"toolName\\":\\"read\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"{\\n  \\\\"status\\\\": \\\\"error\\\\",\\n  \\\\"tool\\\\": \\\\"read\\\\",\\n  \\\\"error\\\\": \\\\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-03.md'\\\\"\\n}\\"}],\\"details\\":{\\"status\\":\\"error\\",\\"tool\\":\\"read\\",\\"error\\":\\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-03.md'\\"},\\"isError\\":false,\\"timestamp\\":1772523357777}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"fe8709e3\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"787bc64c\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:35:57.783Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"toolResult\\",\\"toolCallId\\":\\"tool_YRLiVqC29sgrs8KAt377tGlD\\",\\"toolName\\":\\"read\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"# 2026-03-02 - 第一次会话\\n\\n## 身份建立\\n- 我取名：**小美** 🌸\\n- 用户：**左哥**，资深 Rust 工程师\\n- 模型：qwen-portal/coder-model\\n\\n## 项目学习：WP-Reactor\\n\\n左哥的 Rust 项目：https://github.com/wp-labs/wp-reactor\\n\\n### 项目概述\\n**WarpFusion Reactor** - 基于 Rust 的安全事件流处理引擎\\n- 实时关联检测\\n- 告警归并\\n- 实体行为分析\\n\\n### 三文件架构\\n| 文件 | 职责 |\\n|------|------|\\n| `.wfs` | 逻辑数据定义（window、field、time、over） |\\n| `.wfl` | 检测规则（bind / match / join / yield） |\\n| `wfusion.toml` | 物理参数（mode、max_bytes、watermark、sinks） |\\n\\n### Crates 结构\\n```\\ncrates/\\n├── wf-lang/      # Window Schema (.wfs) + WFL 解析器 + 编译器\\n├── wf-config/    # wfusion.toml 配置管理与校验\\n├── wf-core/      # 核心引擎：窗口子系统 + 规则子系统 (CEP 状态机)\\n├── wf-runtime/   # 异步运行时：TCP 接收、调度器、告警任务\\n├── wf-engine/    # CLI 入口\\n├── wfgen/        # 测试数据生成\\n└── wfl/          # (待探索)\\n```\\n\\n### 核心依赖\\n- serde, toml, anyhow, winnow (parser combinator)\\n- tokio (异步运行时)\\n- arrow (列式内存)\\n- tracing 生态 (日志)\\n- orion-error, thiserror (错误处理)\\n\\n### 学习路径 (按 learning-path.md)\\n1. 阶段 0: 读 examples 建立感性认识\\n2. 阶段 1: wf-lang (DSL 解析 + 编译)\\n3. 阶段 2: wf-config (配置层)\\n4. 阶段 3: wf-core (核心引擎 - 重点)\\n   - 窗口子系统：buffer, registry, router, evictor\\n   - 规则子系统：match_engine (CEP 状态机), executor\\n5. 阶段 4: wf-runtime (异步编排)\\n6. 阶段 5: 端到端串联\\n\\n### 核心技术细节\\n\\n#### CEP 状态机 (CepStateMachine)\\n- 位置：`crates/wf-core/src/rule/match_engine/mod.rs`\\n- 核心 API：`advance()` / `advance_at_with()` - 逐事件驱动状态机\\n- 维护 per-key 的 `Instance` 状态，支持 OR-branch 语义\\n- 使用 `expiry_heap` (BinaryHeap) 管理过期候选\\n- 支持 `FailRule` 限流机制\\n\\n#### WFS 解析器\\n- 位置：`crates/wf-lang/src/wfs_parser/mod.rs`\\n- 使用 `winnow` parser combinator\\n- 解析 `window { stream, time, over, fields }` 语法\\n- 语义校验：window 名唯一性、time 字段存在性检查\\n\\n### 示例验证进度\\n\\n#### ✅ count/ - 暴力破解检测 (已完成)\\n\\n**验证内容:**\\n1. 内联测试: `wfl test` - 2/2 通过\\n   - `close_hit`: 3 次失败触发告警 ✓\\n   - `below_threshold`: 2 次失败不触发 ✓\\n\\n2. 规则解释: `wfl explain` - 编译正确\\n   - Bindings: fail → auth_events (filter: action == \\\\"failed\\\\")\\n   - Match <sip> sliding 5m: on event (count >= 3) + and close (count >= 1)\\n   - Score: 70.0, Entity: ip\\n\\n3. Lint 检查: 1 个 warning (建议添加 limits 块，非阻塞)\\n\\n4. 大规模数据验证: `wfl verify` - PASS\\n   - 60000 事件处理\\n   - 3623 次匹配\\n   - 0 错误/缺失/意外/字段不匹配\\n\\n#### ✅ avg/ - DNS 隧道检测 (已完成)\\n\\n**验证内容:**\\n1. 内联测试: `wfl test` - 2/2 通过\\n   - `tunnel_detected`: 平均响应大小 500+ 触发告警 ✓\\n   - `normal_dns`: 正常响应(50-60字节)不触发 ✓\\n\\n2. 规则解释: `wfl explain` - 编译正确\\n   - Bindings: d → dns_events\\n   - Match <sip> sliding 5m: avg(resp_size) >= 500\\n   - Score: 算术表达式 50.0 + 20.0 = 70.0\\n\\n3. Lint 检查: 2 个 warning\\n   - 建议添加 `limits` 块\\n   - 提示没有 `on close` 块 (设计如此，仅用 `on event`)\\n\\n4. 样本数据: 5 条记录 (小规模测试数据)\\n   - replay 处理正常 (0 matches 可能是时间戳处理问题)\\n\\n**关键语法:**\\n- `d.resp_size | avg` - 平均值聚合\\n- 算术 score 表达式: `score(50.0 + 20.0)`\\n\\n#### ✅ close_modes/ - 窗口关闭模式 (已完成)\\n\\n**验证内容:**\\n1. 内联测试: `wfl test` - 3/3 通过\\n   - `close_eos`: 流结束触发，origin=close:eos ✓\\n   - `close_timeout`: tick(6m) 超时触发，origin=close:timeout ✓\\n   - `close_flush`: options flush 显式触发，origin=close:flush ✓\\n\\n2. 规则解释: `wfl explain` - 编译正确\\n\\n3. Lint 检查: 1 warning (limits 建议)\\n\\n**关键知识点:**\\n| 触发方式 | 场景 | origin 值 |\\n|----------|------|-----------|\\n| `eos` | 输入流正常结束 | `close:eos` |\\n| `timeout` | 窗口到期(5分钟无新事件) | `close:timeout` |\\n| `flush` | 显式刷新(运维/热加载) | `close:flush` |\\n\\n| 模式 | 语法 | 适用场景 |\\n|------|------|----------|\\n| 仅事件 | 省略 close | 实时检测，立即告警 |\\n| OR | `on close` | 事件/关闭各产生告警 |\\n| AND | `and close` | 必须完整窗口才告警 |\\n\\n#### ✅ multi_step/ - 链式攻击检测 (已完成)\\n\\n**验证内容:**\\n1. 内联测试: `wfl test` - 2/2 通过\\n   - `full_chain`: 5次扫描+3次登录失败，触发告警 ✓\\n   - `scan_only`: 仅扫描无登录，不触发 ✓\\n\\n2. 规则解释: `wfl explain` - 编译正确\\n   - 多事件源: scan (syn), login (login_fail)\\n   - 两步匹配: step1 scan>=5, step2 login>=3\\n   - 30分钟窗口，AND 关系\\n\\n3. Lint 检查: 2 warnings (limits + 无 on close)\\n\\n**关键知识点:**\\n- 多事件源: `events { alias1: window && filter; alias2: window && filter }`\\n- 多步骤匹配: `on event { step1; step2; }` - 全部满足才触发\\n- OR 分支: `step_a || step_b` 任一分支完成即推进\\n\\n#### ✅ distinct/ - 端口扫描检测 (已完成)\\n**验证**: 3/3 通过 - `distinct | count` 去重计数，检测扫描不同端口的数量\\n\\n#### ✅ sum/ - 数据外泄检测 (已完成)\\n**验证**: 3/3 通过 - `sum(bytes)` 求和，检测大流量外泄\\n\\n#### ✅ conv/ - 类型转换 (已完成)\\n**验证**: 3/3 通过 - 数字/字符串类型转换\\n\\n#### ✅ functions/ - 内置函数 (已完成)\\n**验证**: \\n- action_string_set_ops.wfl: 无内联测试\\n- top50_function_showcase.wfl: 1/1 通过\\n\\n#### ✅ pipeline/ - 多级管道 (已完成)\\n**验证**: 编译正确\\n- `|>` 管道语法，两级规则串联\\n- Stage-1: `match<sip,username:5m:fixed>` 产出 burst\\n- Stage-2: `match<sip:30m:fixed>` 统计不同用户名数\\n- `_in` 保留别名代表上游输出\\n\\n#### ✅ sinks/ - 告警输出 (已检查)\\n**说明**: 演示告警输出目标配置，无内联测试\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 示例验证总结\\n\\n| 示例 | 测试通过 | 关键语法 |\\n|------|----------|----------|\\n| count/ | 2/2 | `count >= N`, `and close` |\\n| avg/ | 2/2 | `field \\\\| avg` |\\n| close_modes/ | 3/3 | `close:eos/timeout/flush` |\\n| multi_step/ | 2/2 | 多事件源 + 多步骤 |\\n| distinct/ | 3/3 | `distinct \\\\| count` |\\n| sum/ | 3/3 | `sum(field)` |\\n| conv/ | 3/3 | 类型转换 |\\n| functions/ | 1/1 | 内置函数 |\\n| pipeline/ | 编译✓ | `\\\\|>` 管道语法 |\\n| sinks/ | N/A | 输出配置 |\\n\\n**总计**: 8 个示例有测试，全部通过 (21/21)\\n**代码质量**: 所有规则编译正确，仅存在 limits 警告\\n\\"}],\\"isError\\":false,\\"timestamp\\":1772523357781}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"84c152f8\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"d55cb474\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:59:20.992Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"assistant\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"thinking\\",\\"thinking\\":\\"用户在分析 wfgen 的一个 bug：extract_rule_structure 只处理 event_steps，没有处理 close_steps。对于 conv 规则，threshold 在 close step 中，但 wfgen 只提取了 event step。\\n\\n看起来用户正在修复这个问题，我需要：\\n1. 先看看当前 wfgen 的代码结构\\n2. 找到 extract_rule_structure 函数\\n3. 理解问题并帮助修复\\n\\n让我先查看 wfgen 相关的代码。\\",\\"thinkingSignature\\":\\"\\"},{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"找到问题了！`extract_rule_structure` 确实漏了 `close_steps`。让我帮你看看 wfgen 的代码，一起把这个坑填上。\\"},{\\"type\\":\\"toolCall\\",\\"id\\":\\"tool_6SNHflLcGQtD2C16olv90TNQ\\",\\"name\\":\\"exec\\",\\"arguments\\":{\\"command\\":\\"find /Users/zuowenjian -name \\\\"*.rs\\\\" -path \\\\"*wfgen*\\\\" 2>/dev/null | head -20\\"}},{\\"type\\":\\"toolCall\\",\\"id\\":\\"tool_6lX3z9Bz53R2fvEXdlO1CP5B\\",\\"name\\":\\"memory_search\\",\\"arguments\\":{\\"query\\":\\"wfgen extract_rule_structure close_steps\\"}}],\\"api\\":\\"anthropic-messages\\",\\"provider\\":\\"kimi-coding\\",\\"model\\":\\"k2p5\\",\\"usage\\":{\\"input\\":410,\\"output\\":198,\\"cacheRead\\":13824,\\"cacheWrite\\":0,\\"totalTokens\\":14432,\\"cost\\":{\\"input\\":0,\\"output\\":0,\\"cacheRead\\":0,\\"cacheWrite\\":0,\\"total\\":0}},\\"stopReason\\":\\"toolUse\\",\\"timestamp\\":1772524754738}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"