{ wp_event_id: 443603477540769497 id: "335efe1b" message/api: "anthropic-messages" message/content[0]/thinking: "从 `openclaw status` 的输出中，我可以看到 Sessions 部分显示了 token 使用情况：\n\n```\n│ agent:main:main                                  │ direct │ just now │ k2p5         │ 34k/262k (13%) · 🗄️ 96% cached │\n```\n\n这表明：\n- 当前使用了 34k tokens\n- 上下文窗口是 262k\n- 使用了 13%\n- 96% 是缓存的\n\n但我需要找到更详细的 cost/usage 信息。让我检查是否有 history 或 session 相关的命令可以查看成本。" message/content[0]/thinkingSignature: "" message/content[0]/type: "thinking" message/content[1]/arguments/query: "token usage cost model pricing billing" message/content[1]/id: "tool_uQYCSVHXylnZDL177tdEzWM0" message/content[1]/name: "memory_search" message/content[1]/type: "toolCall" message/model: "k2p5" message/provider: "kimi-coding" message/role: "assistant" message/stopReason: "toolUse" message/timestamp: 1773799776247 message/usage/cacheRead: 36608 message/usage/cacheWrite: 0 message/usage/cost/cacheRead: 0 message/usage/cost/cacheWrite: 0 message/usage/cost/input: 0 message/usage/cost/output: 0 message/usage/cost/total: 0 message/usage/input: 1086 message/usage/output: 143 message/usage/totalTokens: 37837 parentId: "5831ffbc" timestamp: "2026-03-18T02:09:41.997Z" type: "message" wp_src_key: "file_1" access_source: "../openclaw/target_data/raw_log.dat" }
