{ wp_event_id: 443603477540769499 id: "c974a8f2" message/api: "anthropic-messages" message/content[0]/thinking: "让我查看更多关于 session 的命令，或者查看是否有 `/status` 命令在 chat 中可用。从之前的 system prompt 中我看到有 `session_status` 工具可以显示使用信息。" message/content[0]/thinkingSignature: "" message/content[0]/type: "thinking" message/content[1]/text: "从 `openclaw status` 可以看到当前 session 的 token 使用情况：\n\n```\n│ agent:main:main │ direct │ just now │ k2p5 │ 34k/262k (13%) · 🗄️ 96% cached │\n```\n\n显示使用了 **34k/262k** tokens（13%），其中 96% 是缓存的。\n\n如果你想在聊天中获取更详细的消耗信息，可以使用：\n\n```\n/session_status\n```\n\n或者使用 `/status` 命令，它会显示：\n- 当前模型\n- Token 使用量/上下文窗口大小\n- 使用百分比\n- 缓存命中率\n\nOpenClaw 默认使用 **Kimi k2p5** 模型（上下文窗口 262k），目前似乎没有内置的按模型成本计算功能，主要通过 token 使用量和上下文百分比来监控。" message/content[1]/type: "text" message/model: "k2p5" message/provider: "kimi-coding" message/role: "assistant" message/stopReason: "stop" message/timestamp: 1773799782275 message/usage/cacheRead: 37632 message/usage/cacheWrite: 0 message/usage/cost/cacheRead: 0 message/usage/cost/cacheWrite: 0 message/usage/cost/input: 0 message/usage/cost/output: 0 message/usage/cost/total: 0 message/usage/input: 252 message/usage/output: 215 message/usage/totalTokens: 38099 parentId: "9034d507" timestamp: "2026-03-18T02:09:50.693Z" type: "message" wp_src_key: "file_1" access_source: "../openclaw/target_data/raw_log.dat" }
{ wp_event_id: 443603477540769500 id: "6b42761d" message/content[0]/text: "Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \\"label\\": \\"openclaw-control-ui\\",\n  \\"id\\": \\"openclaw-control-ui\\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-03-18 10:12 GMT+8] 如何知识，调用了那些工具？" message/content[0]/type: "text" message/role: "user" message/timestamp: 1773799966938 parentId: "c974a8f2" timestamp: "2026-03-18T02:12:46.939Z" type: "message" wp_src_key: "file_1" access_source: "../openclaw/target_data/raw_log.dat" }
{ wp_event_id: 443603477540769501 id: "a13b6540" message/api: "anthropic-messages" message/content[0]/thinking: "用户想知道如何查看调用了哪些工具。让我检查一下 OpenClaw 中关于工具调用的日志或追踪功能。" message/content[0]/thinkingSignature: "" message/content[0]/type: "thinking" message/content[1]/arguments/command: "openclaw logs --limit 50 --json 2>/dev/null | grep -i \\"tool\\" | head -20" message/content[1]/id: "tool_Qqwyd2gxEAwTztXGR5L6wEbO" message/content[1]/name: "exec" message/content[1]/type: "toolCall" message/model: "k2p5" message/provider: "kimi-coding" message/role: "assistant" message/stopReason: "toolUse" message/timestamp: 1773799966938 message/usage/cacheRead: 34816 message/usage/cacheWrite: 0 message/usage/cost/cacheRead: 0 message/usage/cost/cacheWrite: 0 message/usage/cost/input: 0 message/usage/cost/output: 0 message/usage/cost/total: 0 message/usage/input: 3049 message/usage/output: 67 message/usage/totalTokens: 37932 parentId: "6b42761d" timestamp: "2026-03-18T02:12:51.265Z" type: "message" wp_src_key: "file_1" access_source: "../openclaw/target_data/raw_log.dat" }
