\\"}}],\\"api\\":\\"anthropic-messages\\",\\"provider\\":\\"kimi-coding\\",\\"model\\":\\"k2p5\\",\\"usage\\":{\\"input\\":209,\\"output\\":88,\\"cacheRead\\":14592,\\"cacheWrite\\":0,\\"totalTokens\\":14889,\\"cost\\":{\\"input\\":0,\\"output\\":0,\\"cacheRead\\":0,\\"cacheWrite\\":0,\\"total\\":0}},\\"stopReason\\":\\"toolUse\\",\\"timestamp\\":1772524787918}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"2b277e03\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"d0f55275\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:59:51.041Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"toolResult\\",\\"toolCallId\\":\\"tool_wouJQCzcSovwSLxhGmrAJAi0\\",\\"toolName\\":\\"read\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"{\\n  \\\\"status\\\\": \\\\"error\\\\",\\n  \\\\"tool\\\\": \\\\"read\\\\",\\n  \\\\"error\\\\": \\\\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/zuowenjian/wp-reactor/crates/wfgen/src/main.rs'\\\\"\\n}\\"}],\\"details\\":{\\"status\\":\\"error\\",\\"tool\\":\\"read\\",\\"error\\":\\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/zuowenjian/wp-reactor/crates/wfgen/src/main.rs'\\"},\\"isError\\":false,\\"timestamp\\":1772524791036}}\n/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/feed9957-3e22-42db-b2e2-5ef3ebd5fd2b.jsonl.reset.2026-03-17T07-06-16.790Z:{\\"type\\":\\"message\\",\\"id\\":\\"04100a49\\",\\"parentId\\":\\"2b277e03\\",\\"timestamp\\":\\"2026-03-03T07:59:51.060Z\\",\\"message\\":{\\"role\\":\\"toolResult\\",\\"toolCallId\\":\\"tool_bER6Ta8eeXafJwzg6eFUYV3d\\",\\"toolName\\":\\"exec\\",\\"content\\":[{\\"type\\":\\"text\\",\\"text\\":\\"path not found\\"}],\\"details\\":{\\"status\\":\\"completed\\",\\"exitCode\\":0,\\"durationMs\\":11,\\"aggregated\\":\\"path not found\\",\\"cwd\\":\\"/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace\\"},\\"isError\\":false,\\"timestamp\\":1772524791058}}" message/details/cwd: "/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace" message/details/durationMs: 27 message/details/exitCode: 0 message/details/status: "completed" message/isError: false message/role: "toolResult" message/timestamp: 1773799990894 message/toolCallId: "tool_HcbuL7dvNL0GRwNJrBtmcpyt" message/toolName: "exec" parentId: "f509d59b" timestamp: "2026-03-18T02:13:10.898Z" type: "message" wp_src_key: "file_1" access_source: "../openclaw/target_data/raw_log.dat" }
{ wp_event_id: 443603477540769509 id: "fba61f17" message/api: "anthropic-messages" message/content[0]/thinking: "很好，我从会话文件中看到了详细的工具调用记录。日志中包含了 `toolCall` 和 `toolResult` 类型的消息，记录了每个工具的调用和返回结果。\n\n让我总结一下如何查看工具调用。" message/content[0]/thinkingSignature: "" message/content[0]/type: "thinking" message/content[1]/text: "从会话存储文件中可以看到，**工具调用信息被完整记录在 session 的 JSONL 文件中**。\n\n## 如何查看工具调用\n\n### 1. 会话历史文件位置\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/<session-id>.jsonl\n```\n\n### 2. 工具调用结构\n\n每个工具调用记录为 JSON 对象，包含以下类型：\n\n| 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `toolCall` | AI 发起工具调用 |\n| `toolResult` | 工具执行结果返回 |\n\n### 3. 示例结构\n\n**工具调用 (`toolCall`)**：\n```json\n{\n  \\"type\\": \\"toolCall\\",\n  \\"id\\": \\"tool_jbjOB39KKxRnTiXfkVlnBn1a\\",\n  \\"name\\": \\"read\\",\n  \\"arguments\\": {\n    \\"file_path\\": \\"/Users/zuowenjian/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**工具结果 (`toolResult`)**：\n```json\n{\n  \\"type\\": \\"toolResult\\",\n  \\"toolCallId\\": \\"tool_jbjOB39KKxRnTiXfkVlnBn1a\\",\n  \\"toolName\\": \\"read\\",\n  \\"content\\": [...],\n  \\"isError\\": false\n}\n```\n\n### 4. 查看方式\n\n```bash\n# 查看最新会话的工具调用\nls -la ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/\n\n# 查看具体会话的工具调用记录\ncat ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/<session-id>.jsonl | grep \\"toolCall\\"\n\n# 查看当前会话的工具调用\nopenclaw logs --limit 100 --json 2>/dev/null | grep -E \\"(tool|exec|read|write)\\"\n```\n\n### 5. 通过 CLI 获取会话历史\n\n```bash\n# 查看会话历史（包含工具调用）\nopenclaw sessions history <session-key>\n\n# 或者查看当前活跃会话\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n---\n\n目前 OpenClaw 没有专门的 `tools list` 或 `tools history` 命令，但所有工具调用都详细记录在：\n- **会话 JSONL 文件** 中（持久化存储）\n- **网关日志** 中（运行时记录，包含 `[tools]` 前缀的日志）\n\n你可以直接解析会话文件来获取完整的工具调用链。" message/content[1]/type: "text" message/model: "k2p5" message/provider: "kimi-coding" message/role: "assistant" message/stopReason: "stop" message/timestamp: 1773799990901 message/usage/cacheRead: 39936 message/usage/cacheWrite: 0 message/usage/cost/cacheRead: 0 message/usage/cost/cacheWrite: 0 message/usage/cost/input: 0 message/usage/cost/output: 0 message/usage/cost/total: 0 message/usage/input: 26041 message/usage/output: 541 message/usage/totalTokens: 66518 parentId: "8bd80b2e" timestamp: "2026-03-18T02:13:30.914Z" type: "message" wp_src_key: "file_1" access_source: "../openclaw/target_data/raw_log.dat" }
